{
  "stem": "3605.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had it like an amphitheater hall where we used to have our meetings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was always a guard standing, and if somebody suspicious was passing through the street, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he gave us a special whistle, and we all toned down and kept quiet.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if something was real kind of questionable, there was a shed right close by the-- that hall, where we all went into that shed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from this shed, there was an open board going into another section that was like another block facing another street, and the people just dispersed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, quite a few occasions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because sometimes the German people were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] coming in and walking through the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't even want the Jewish policemen should know too much about our activities, because sometimes their allegiance was also not too much to us, and we were afraid that some information will leak out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Regretfully and sadly, I hate to talk about it, but there were-- in every community, there are good people and bad people, and Jews are no exception.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some that thought that this is their glory and power, when they had that uniform, and they had a rubber stick.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans didn't trust them with a gun, so they used it sometimes when they shouldn't have.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But people are shortsighted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They gave all kind of orders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to be listened to and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they could have been more gentle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But these were exceptions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Other people knew to be in line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But of course you have to be careful for such exceptions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were also [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] trying to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not to cause too much commotion in town.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
